snippet.title: Fast Dust - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Fast Dust is way more then just another racing game, you get a chance to drive amazing and unique cars with true character. 

Race through forest, canyon and old factory city, 70 racetracks to cover, total of 270 miles (430km). Career and Multiplayer. Full controller support.

Prepare your self for Fast Dust!!!

Premiere on STEAM August 22nd 2018: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/891330/Fast_Dust/

More info: http://fastdust.com/
